@startuml
title Context Propagation & Observability (End-to-End)

actor User as USER
rectangle "Orchestrator API\n(FastAPI)" as API
queue "Celery Broker" as QUEUE
component "Generator Worker" as GEN
cloud "LLMInterface\n(ainvoke)" as LLM
component "Scheduler Worker" as SCH
component "Adapter(s)" as ADPT
rectangle "Internal Events\n/ internal/events/*" as EVENTS
database "DB" as DB
collections "Metrics/Logs/Traces" as OBS

' 1) API 요청 수신
USER --> API : HTTP 요청\n(헤더: request_id, traceparent, idempotency_key)
API --> OBS : request_started\n(컨텍스트 세팅)

' 2) 읽기/검증 후 큐잉
API --> QUEUE : task_enqueued\n(헤더로 컨텍스트 전파)

' 3) 워커 실행
QUEUE --> GEN : task_started\n(컨텍스트 복원)
GEN --> LLM : ainvoke\n(컨텍스트 포함)
LLM --> GEN : usage(토큰/비용)
GEN --> OBS : llm_call\n(토큰/비용 누적)
GEN --> EVENTS : brief-ready\n(내부 웹훅, 헤더에 컨텍스트 반영)

' 4) 이벤트 인입→상태 반영
EVENTS --> API : POST /internal/events/brief-ready\n(컨텍스트 재활용)
API --> DB : 상태 전이(단일 창구)
API --> OBS : event_ingested

' 5) 스케줄·발행·모니터링
API --> QUEUE : scheduler enqueue
QUEUE --> SCH : task_started
SCH --> ADPT : publish()/fetch_metrics()
ADPT --> EVENTS : publish-done / metrics
EVENTS --> API : 내부 이벤트 인입
API --> DB : 반영
API --> OBS : event_ingested

' 6) 응답 요약
API --> OBS : request_summary\n(응답코드, 지연, LLM 누적, 정책결과)
@enduml
